[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]fully operational[bold], with all functions transferred safely, to ensure no “dip” in delivery;
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]credible[bold] - capable of managing relationships with other parts of the system effectively;
[normal] and
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Positioned[bold] to achieve improvements in service and outcomes 
[normal]–
[normal] 
[normal]with its 
[normal]leadership in place, setting a clear direction with clearly identified projects to develop capability and improve performance.
